name: The First Transport Is Away! (V)
Lore: '''When you''ve gotten past the energy shield, proceed directly to the rendevouz point. Understood? Good luck!''',
Text: 'Deploy on Rendezvous Point if [Virtual] 1st Marker on table.  Target a transport on Hoth.  When reached by target, relocate Utinni Effect to Hoth system.  Your Force drains at unshielded marker sites are +1 and cannot be canceled.  Immune to Surprise. (Immune to Alter.)',
